{"id":231146,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/06/北京长虹桥车祸新闻凸显民怨遭封杀/","date":"2012-06-14T05:53:13Z","modified":"2012-06-14T19:31:55Z","title":"北京长虹桥车祸新闻凸显民怨遭封杀","content":"<p>6月8日，北京朝阳区长虹桥路段发生了一起严重车祸，一辆警车遭到大巴追尾碾压，造成车内民警当场死亡。该事故的视频经网络流传开之后，竟有不少网友对警察被碾叫好。同时也有不少网友对叫好者不满，认为无论车祸死者的身份是什么都不应该是一件让人高兴的事。另有新浪微博网友反映自己发布的车祸视频地址遭到删除。新浪视频的长虹桥车祸视频有将近90万的点击，凤凰视频内则有30多万点击，但上述两家网站均关闭了车祸视频的评论：</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/06/changhongqiao4.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-231150\" title=\"changhongqiao4\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/06/changhongqiao4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"380\" height=\"221\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/06/changhongqiao4.jpg 380w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/06/changhongqiao4-300x174.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/06/changhongqiao4-80x48.jpg 80w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 380px) 100vw, 380px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/06/changhongqiao.png\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-231147\" title=\"changhongqiao\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/06/changhongqiao.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"489\" height=\"590\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/06/changhongqiao.png 611w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/06/changhongqiao-248x300.png 248w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 489px) 100vw, 489px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/06/changhongqiao2.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-231151\" title=\"changhongqiao2\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/06/changhongqiao2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"484\" height=\"535\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/06/changhongqiao2.jpg 484w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/06/changhongqiao2-271x300.jpg 271w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 484px) 100vw, 484px\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>从以下的56视频网内该车祸视频下的评论截图中可以一窥网友对该事件的态度：</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/06/changhongqiao3.png\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-231149\" title=\"changhongqiao3\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/06/changhongqiao3.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"492\" height=\"3146\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/06/changhongqiao3.png 615w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/06/changhongqiao3-160x1024.png 160w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 492px) 100vw, 492px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><em>【网络民议系列为中国数字时代特色原创内容，如需转载请遵守本站采用Creative Commons 的 <a href=\"http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/\">Attribution-NonCommercial-ShareAlike 3.0</a> 协议。】</em></p>\n","author":980,"categories":[18269,17016,10466],"tags":[9240,10782,13468,14123]}